    "text": "♪ My name is who ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.1,
    "endTime": 16.6,
    "text": "♪ My name is ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.6,
    "endTime": 20.900000000000002,
    "text": "♪ You used to call me on my cell phone ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.9,
    "endTime": 22.599999999999998,
    "text": "Guys, we're on, right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.6,
    "endTime": 26.5,
    "text": "Now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.5,
    "endTime": 27.2,
    "text": "Stop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.2,
    "endTime": 29.24,
    "text": "I need big shows, big ideas."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.3,
    "endTime": 32.2,
    "text": "Hey, I have a big one, with Clay Calloway."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.2,
    "endTime": 34.400000000000006,
    "text": "Whoa, whoa you know Calloway?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.4,
    "endTime": 38.5,
    "text": "Clay Calloway is a recluse, no one's seen him for 15 years."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.5,
    "endTime": 40.8,
    "text": "I'll give you three weeks to get the show up and running."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.8,
    "endTime": 42.251,
    "text": "I won't let you down, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.251,
    "endTime": 46.3,
    "text": "Better not or I'll throw you off the roof."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.3,
    "endTime": 48.382,
    "text": "♪ There's nothing holding me back ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.841,
    "endTime": 54.2,
    "text": "I have dreamt of performing in Redshore City since I was a little kid!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.2,
    "endTime": 56.2,
    "text": "♪ There's nothing holding me back ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.2,
    "endTime": 59.900000000000006,
    "text": "This is Redshore City, not your little local theater."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.9,
    "endTime": 61.3,
    "text": "He's freaking me out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.3,
    "endTime": 66.3,
    "text": "Tippy toes, tippy toes. I don't see your tippy toes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.3,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "This is my daughter, Porsha, she wants to meet Calloway, big fan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.0,
    "endTime": 71.8,
    "text": "My assistant is on her way to meet him right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.0,
    "endTime": 72.8,
    "text": "♪ Wake up, wake up ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.8,
    "endTime": 74.8,
    "text": "♪ Grab a brush and put a little make-up ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.8,
    "endTime": 76.7,
    "text": "♪ Hide the scars to  fade away the shake-up ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.7,
    "endTime": 78.4,
    "text": "♪ Why'd you leave the keys upon the table ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.4,
    "endTime": 80.10000000000001,
    "text": "Your destination is on the right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.1,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "On the right, okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.0,
    "endTime": 85.5,
    "text": "♪ There's nothing holding me back ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.5,
    "endTime": 89.0,
    "text": "If you could just give me some dance lessons, you would be saving my life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.0,
    "endTime": 91.3,
    "text": "How do I know that you're not a weirdo?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.3,
    "endTime": 97.0,
    "text": "How do I know that you're legit?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 98.3,
    "text": "♪ Oh, I've been shaking ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.3,
    "endTime": 100.3,
    "text": "♪ I love it when you go crazy ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.3,
    "endTime": 102.5,
    "text": "-♪ You take all my inhibitions ♪- What are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.5,
    "endTime": 106.05,
    "text": "♪ Baby, there's nothing holding me back ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.064,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "I knew you were a weirdo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 108.6,
    "text": "Playback."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.6,
    "endTime": 110.89999999999999,
    "text": "♪ He says that she's never afraid ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.0,
    "endTime": 115.907,
    "text": "And here she is, the star of our show, Rosita."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.907,
    "endTime": 117.8,
    "text": "Oh my gosh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.8,
    "endTime": 118.7,
    "text": "Can I try?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.7,
    "endTime": 119.2,
    "text": "No, no, no, no, no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.2,
    "endTime": 121.913,
    "text": "♪ This girl is on fire ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.913,
    "endTime": 124.89999999999999,
    "text": "She's afraid. She'll never be able to play the part."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.9,
    "endTime": 134.9,
    "text": "Maybe this is for the best, I'll write you another part, Rosita."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.9,
    "endTime": 137.20000000000002,
    "text": "There he is, Clay Calloway."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.2,
    "endTime": 138.5,
    "text": "Go away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.764,
    "endTime": 140.20000000000002,
    "text": "Don't you miss the music?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.2,
    "endTime": 141.7,
    "text": "You just need to play again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.808,
    "endTime": 151.0,
    "text": "No, I can't! I haven't even heard one of my songs in over 15 years and for good reason."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.7,
    "endTime": 164.0,
    "text": "♪ I have climbed the highest mountains ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.2,
    "endTime": 168.42999999999998,
    "text": "♪ I have run through the fields ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.5,
    "endTime": 169.8,
    "text": "It's okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.2,
    "endTime": 171.6,
    "text": "♪ But I still ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.6,
    "endTime": 172.79999999999998,
    "text": "Your songs will carry you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.8,
    "endTime": 174.8,
    "text": "♪ Haven't found ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.8,
    "endTime": 175.8,
    "text": "Just sing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.8,
    "endTime": 177.13000000000002,
    "text": "♪ What I'm looking for ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.2,
    "endTime": 181.5,
    "text": "There's only one way left to go and that's up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.5,
    "endTime": 184.8,
    "text": "♪ Still haven't found ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.8,
    "endTime": 187.70000000000002,
    "text": "Dream big dreams."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.7,
    "endTime": 192.7,
    "text": "That's what they always said, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.7,
    "endTime": 193.89999999999998,
    "text": "♪ But I still ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.069,
    "endTime": 198.03099999999998,
    "text": "There's always a choice, just never had the guts to make the right one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.031,
    "endTime": 208.3,
    "text": "♪ What I'm looking for ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.3,
